# ---------------------------------------------------------------
# Git ignore file for the novel-studio project
# This file defines which files and directories should not be tracked
# by Git. It focuses on excluding build artefacts, temporary files,
# virtual environments and intermediate data produced by the writing
# pipeline.

## General Python artefacts
*.pyc
__pycache__/
.pytest_cache/
.mypy_cache/

## Virtual environments
.venv/
venv/

## Editor / OS metadata
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
*.swo
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

## Application logs and temporary data
02_working/logs/
02_working/context/
02_working/test_artifacts/

## Intermediate drafts, rewrites and reviews
02_working/drafts/
02_working/reviews/
02_working/canon_updates/
02_working/outlines/

## Auto-generated tasks and life notes
01_inputs/tasks/generated/
01_inputs/life_notes/

## Candidate chapters and state history (locked output only retains final versions)
03_locked/candidates/
03_locked/state/history/

## Build & packaging artefacts
build/
dist/
*.egg-info/

## Compressed archives
*.zip
*.tar.gz
*.tar

# End of .gitignore